good analysis!

    Setzer> The following definition for qqline reflects this point:

    Setzer> function (y, ...)
    Setzer> {
    Setzer> y <- y[!is.na(y)]
    Setzer> n <- length(y)
    Setzer> y <- quantile(y, c(0.25, 0.75))
    Setzer> x <- quantile(qnorm(ppoints(n)),c(0.25, 0.75))
