R> m <- matrix (c(6.8, 2.4, 2.4, 8.2), nrow=2)
R> eigen (m)
$values
[1] 10  5

$vectors
     [,1] [,2]
[1,]  0.6  0.8
[2,]  0.8 -0.6


I found this by running "make check" which also stumbles over svd.
Please let me know how I can help to investigate this.

